<p>held in facilities under 
the control of their 
interrogators or 
investigators for more 
than the time required 
by law to obtain a 
judicial warrant or 
pretrial detention, 
which <b>normally 
should not exceed a 
period of 48 hours</b>. 
After this period they 
should be <b>transferred 
to a pretrial facility 
under a different 
