<p>&#8226; To review and periodically revise the 
existing Criminal Justice Reform 
Strategy 
</p>
<p>&#8226; To coordinate intergovernmental 
activities in the elaboration of the 
Criminal Justice Reform Strategy; 
and 
</p>
<p>&#8226; To elaborate proposals and 
recommendations regarding issues 
related to penal reform, probation, 
juvenile justice and legal aid 
</p>
<p>&#8226; The members of the Council are high 
